          </li>
          <li style="padding: 0; margin: 0; display: inline-block; line-height: 18px; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: top">
            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
              <tr>
                <td valign="top">
                  <a href="https://t.me/Mrzesttee" target="_blank"
                    ><img src="https://media.zesttee.com/cms/telegram-icon_5b4730a45885_1954-a.png" width="18" alt="Telegram"
